title: MUMBLE_ADD_VOICE_TARGET_PLAYER_BY_SERVER_ID
content:
0x25F2B65F// MumbleAddVoiceTargetPlayerByServerId
void MUMBLE_ADD_VOICE_TARGET_PLAYER_BY_SERVER_ID(int targetId, int serverId);Parameters:targetId: A Mumble voice target ID, ranging from 1..30 (inclusive).serverId: The player's server id.Adds the specified player to the target list for the specified Mumble voice target ID.
